{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"16f96dc9d9","title":"致邓小平电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3eb09626cf","index":0,"year":1948,"month":3,"day":14,"articleId":"16f96dc9d9"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"02e2956d4b","type":"paragraph","text":"致邓小平电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"16f96dc9d9"},{"id":"129447e485","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年3月14日）小平同志：演齐电悉，非常之好，立即转发各地仿照办理。希望你对除唐、陈谢各部及豫皖苏区，凡你处电台能联络的同志，或骑马能送信的同志，或当面接治的同志，将你所说的那些策略观点与政策观点，普遍通知他们，只要有机会就不失时机地指导他们，并要他们向你处反映结果","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"16f96dc9d9"},{"id":"e93e3e22ca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"16f96dc9d9"},{"id":"c15ade3399","type":"paragraph","text":"寅寒[l]宽齐屯，指邓小平3月8日关于新解放区全般的策略与致策问题向中共中央的报告。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"16f96dc9d9"}],"page":{"id":"f21822de9a","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"16f96dc9d9","start":161,"end":161}}}},"__N_SSG":true}